{"tid":1130310,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(美容jj入）求意見","createTime":"2019-04-29T02:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T12:40:06.000Z","uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"65b952f237d440358f1ec6149297c996f9771fca","tid":1130310,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T02:58:00.000Z","msg":"想問前景行內同人工邊間做學徒最好？<br />\n<br />\n問左一個美容師佢話英格蜜兒train得有質素同出黎行入面比較搶手。<br />\n我google完差唔多全行學徒最低<br />\n<br />\n我手上有幾間美容院offer，我應該點選擇？<br />\n我性格好慢熱，我就想做公數多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有邊幾間美容/專櫃係公數形式出人工？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果學徒黎講<br />\n12000蚊頭3個月<br />\n3個月14000<br />\n6個月就18000<br />\n 時間就6日 10h<br />\n呢個價係正常學徒價定已經俾人壓價 ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多問題，唔該大家"},{"pid":"2c6bab45e9540a3a272a437f0894c1b8ce8e474e","tid":1130310,"uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"我個日去面試超多靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪唔靚唔洗發展得好？<br />\n連hr都話我點解眼神唔夠無咩自信<br />\n但佢請左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講自問個樣唔得，我都係見工前一日先買化妝品唔太中意打扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我已經搵工搵左成4個月，我見都"},{"pid":"2159a245ba62ae8db28a4d170e1d1a27fd17bcdf","tid":1130310,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c6bab45e9540a3a272a437f0894c1b8ce8e474e","tid":1130310,"uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"我個日去面試超多靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪唔靚唔洗發展得好？<br />\n連hr都話我點解眼神唔夠無咩自信<br />\n但佢請左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講自問個樣唔得，我都係見工前一日先買化妝品唔太中意打扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我已經搵工搵左成4個月，我見都"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:13:37.000Z","msg":"親都係毒撚工同好等人用（銀行文員,pccw，學資），但全部唔請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一係就有offer臨尾返工前3日打黎話搵人頂左我個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年12月搵到而加先去send美容行業，去見既全部有哂offer,我個心理只係覺得唔想失業（份約去到5月）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsend極唔知點解得化妝品護膚品美容學徒請我，連10000既文員都唔要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00c593729a36d6713ce61c90fd4d62e0be1e470","tid":1130310,"uid":182777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:42:38.000Z","msg":"你rxxnex second in左未？"},{"pid":"cd5139151af8c4af97d1d1ddd93a0f8f217fd026","tid":1130310,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e00c593729a36d6713ce61c90fd4d62e0be1e470","tid":1130310,"uid":182777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:42:38.000Z","msg":"你rxxnex second in左未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:11:39.000Z","msg":"無打黎 聽日就第七日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該都過唔到<br />\n應該衰左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />男人in 都預左請 靚女，<br />\n得英格xx同btp<br />\n同兩間地區美容店offer,<br />\n有個專櫃就黎緊in <br />\n<br />\n上黎上問下邊間好？<br />\n你點知我有去in rexnex"},{"pid":"020f1533d0473824a7aae270d6efb2399addd91f","tid":1130310,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e00c593729a36d6713ce61c90fd4d62e0be1e470","tid":1130310,"uid":182777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:42:38.000Z","msg":"你rxxnex second in左未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:12:17.000Z","msg":"人工呢間最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcbdfa0e779bb724eb16211fef321d995004e31","tid"